{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-417-reciprocal-cycles-ii","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Problem 417: Recipročni ciklusi II","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dio broja ima 1 na svojoj najvišoj poziciji/lancu. Predstavljanje ovih delova u decimalnom sistemu sa lancima od 2 do 10 je prikazano:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{2}  = 0.5 \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{3}  = 0.(3) \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{4}  = 0.25 \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{5}  = 0.2 \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{6}  = 0.1(6) \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{7}  = 0.(142857) \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{8}  = 0.125 \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{9}  = 0.(1) \\\\\n&#x26; \\frac{1}{10} = 0.1 \\\\\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Gde $0.1(6)$ znači $0.166666\\ldots$, i ima ciklus od 1 cifre. Može se videti da $\\frac{1}{7}$ ima ciklus od 6 cifara.</p>\n<p>Jedinične frakcije čiji imeniok nema druge prime faktore osim 2 i/ili 5 ne smatraju se da imaju periodični ciklus. Definišemo dužinu periodičnog ciklusa tih jediničnih frakcija as 0.</p>\n<p>Neka $L(n)$ označava dužinu periodičnog ciklusa za $\\frac{1}{n}$. Data je informacija da $\\sum L(n)$ for $3 ≤ n ≤ 1\\,000\\,000$ iznosi $55\\,535\\,191\\,115$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $\\sum L(n)$ for $3 ≤ n ≤ 100,000,000$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f50d1000cf542c51001f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302086,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-417-reciprocal-cycles-ii"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function reciprocalCyclesTwo() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nreciprocalCyclesTwo();","head":null,"tail":nu